# moveFiles

Move specified files to the target folder

## Usage

```js
await dataverseConnector.runOS({
  method: SYSTEM_CALL.moveFiles,
  params: {
    targetFolderId,
    sourceIndexFileIds: [],
  },
});
```

## Parameters

- `string` - destination folder id
- `Array<string>` - Id of files to move

## Returns

```js
{
    movedFiles: Array<File>,
    sourceFolders: Array<StructuredFolder>,
    targetFolder: StructuredFolder,
    allFolders: Array<StructuredFolder>
}
```
